{"tid":1183835,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【手刃親兒】憂兒子步川崎兇手後塵殺小學生 76歲日本前高官菜刀捅死44歲隱蔽兒子","createTime":"2019-06-03T08:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T09:05:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c827d8ab810b731901edc93b1b95b3b4e04d2da","tid":1183835,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"日本川崎巿早前有兇徒亂斬等校車的學生及行人之後自刎，造成一名小六女生及一名男子死亡，17人受傷，此案更可能間接導致新一宗倫常兇案。日本前駐捷克大使熊澤英昭涉嫌殺死自己的兒子被捕，他供稱兒子有暴力傾向，試過向家人「施暴」，最近更抱怨鄰近小學舉行運動會的聲音太吵，他供稱擔心兒子最終會傷害他人，於是決定手刃親兒。<br />\n報道指，熊澤英昭周六於東京的住所親手把44歲的兒子英一郎（Eiichiro，音譯）殺死，他承認用菜刀朝兒子的胸口刺了幾刀，隨後自行向警方報案。警方到場將熊澤英昭拘捕，英一郎送院後證實死亡。<br />\n熊澤英昭與妻子及英一郎同住東京的居所。根據警方消息，熊澤英昭指兒子經常留在家中，缺乏社交生活，並且有暴力傾向，更試過向兩老「施暴」。據稱，案發當天，英一郎曾抱怨鄰近小學舉行運動會的聲音太吵，熊澤英昭擔心兒子會對公眾不利，於是將他殺死。<br />\n76歲的熊澤英昭曾任職日本農林水產省高級官員，並在2005年至2008年擔任日本駐捷克大使。警方正調查事件，懷疑事件起因與長期累積的家庭糾紛有關。一名86歲的鄰居表示：「（熊澤英昭一家）約10年前搬進來，但我從未見過那名兒子。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190603/large/1559543535_e814.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190603%2Flarge%2F1559543535_e814.jpg&h=dd6b1ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190603/59671118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59671118&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewODUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=53de63a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190603%2F59671118&h=1fceda8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190603/59671118</a>"},{"pid":"5065dc2fa937052b9cfb9523ecae9770807f5ac6","tid":1183835,"uid":33653,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"親手解決問題"},{"pid":"803a6e83d64e4a3cf358ff746789c97e9753da92","tid":1183835,"uid":229608,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:44:17.000Z","msg":"真大義滅親<br />\n犧牲自己去坐監，可能救翻佢都無辜者"},{"pid":"a21fa71dbc3f846f9b1b6e4e4a9524231e6bf89a","tid":1183835,"uid":237425,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:48:50.000Z","msg":"呢個老野都知自己縱左條痴線仔出黎<br />\n都係自己親手負責番"},{"pid":"a1d4e2e1a1bd74f94a82cb469661a0585159e748","tid":1183835,"uid":194177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441e1298958c894839e545ec5da495c0a69871f5","tid":1183835,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"日本無青山？"},{"pid":"2d827c597c9dfa873ac6ecdfe6c27f9c24e32ee9","tid":1183835,"uid":123175,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:57:00.000Z","msg":"如果係二戰前<br />\n呢單嘢應該會當喜事咁報<br />\n個老豆應該會畀人奉為父親典範"},{"pid":"3749ae7bd398db6d08781223b68f28fcde87a250","tid":1183835,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:05:33.000Z","msg":"負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}